                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12">
                    <h1 class="h1 jumbotron"> Transitions </h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-9 col-md-9 text-center" role="main">
                    
    <h2 class="h2" id="lunch">Lunch Transition</h2>
    <hr class="subtitle"/>
    <div class="list-group">
        <li class="item">Put away your materials.</li>
        <li class="item">Grab your lunch box/bag/money if you have it.</li>
        <li class="item">Line up in front of the door.</li>
        <li class="item">Wait for me to say go ahead.</li>
        <li class="item">Once I tell you to go ahead you will walk down the hallway respectfully to other classes toward
                        the lunch room.</li>
        <li class="last-item">I will lock the door behind you all so that way you know your things are safe.</li>
    </div>

    <h2 class="h2" id="after-lunch">After Lunch Transition</h2>
    <hr class="subtitle"/>
    <div class="list-group">
        <li class="item">I will take you back to the classroom once you are lined up in the cafeteria and your tables are
                        clean.</li>
        <li class="item">I will unlock the door so you can get our stuff so that you can go to your next class.</li>
    </div>

    <h2 class="h2" id="assembly">Assembly Transition</h2>
    <hr class="subtitle"/>
    <div class="list-group">
        <li class="item">Put materials inside of backpack.</li>
        <li class="item">Grab your backpack.</li>
        <li class="item">Line up in front of the door.</li>
        <li class="item">Wait for me to tell you to go ahead.</li>
        <li class="last-item">I will lock the door behind us.</li>
    </div>

    <h2 class="h2" id="emergency">Emergency Procedures</h2>
    <hr class="subtitle"/>
    <div class="list-group">
        <li class="item">No matter what I will always grab my student roster so that I know each of your lovely faces
                        are safe.</li>
        <li class="item">I will always guide you through what to do for the emergency procedures in a calm manner.
                        Whether it is walk to our destination during a fire drill, or to curl up in a ball during a tornado
                        drill.</li>
        <li class="item">I will stay calm so that way you know that I am prepared and am ready for what is going on.</li>
    </div>

                </div>
